          "order": 2,
          "title": "CERTGRAPH",
          "summary": "CertGraph constructs and crawls the graph of a domain’s SSL certificates. It does this by treating each domain as a node and each certificate alternative node as an edge to another domain node. The tool was created for enumeration via SSL certificates.",
